{"tid":2152060,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"個人觀點時間-中國階級+世界觀列表","createTime":"2020-08-11T17:55:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T02:11:24.000Z","uid":352783,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f602da9ef614c6f3eb2dbd2a7a3741d7e3e5be91","tid":2152060,"uid":352783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T17:55:20.000Z","msg":"眾所9知，中国背叛咗共產主義N世<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n階段壁壘分明，但詳細情況又係點呢？<br />\n以下將會分析一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:<br />\n<br />\n世界觀系列:<br />\n1.俄羅斯(俄爹)<br />\n冇咗俄佬中國又點會有今日呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪先？<br />\n2.歐美各國<br />\n嗱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打嘴炮可以，打真軍？不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<del>送仔女出國緊要D，中國係你班草民先會留低㗎咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></del><br />\n3.友邦(唔包俄羅斯同非洲盟友)<br />\n寧予友邦不予家奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n經濟援助就梗係俾用嚟<del>收買</del>維繫友誼㗎啦，要我留比俾本國人民？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.日韓台<br />\n每日仇恨對象，可以做一千萬個貶義詞每日抹黑佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5.南洋各國及印度<br />\n未開化國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一班馬騮<br />\n呀&hellip;&hellip;好似有個同我地D縣咁上下大嘅國家下嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n6.非洲國家<br />\n冇我地中國carry你有今日？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4b19219ee41ff4979240f24bc9f95d193b09863","tid":2152060,"uid":352783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T18:24:39.000Z","msg":"中國國內階級:<br />\n1.權貴(趙家人)<br />\n中國特權階段，佢地嘅地位冇需多講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一條友成功，成村人光榮！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 居於中國嘅外國人<br />\n重點統戰對象，點可以怠慢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.北京城區户籍居民<br />\n首都天龍人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />北大清華特別易入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />贏在起跑線，理想更易達到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.港澳台同胞<br />\n原因同居華外國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實港台明星去中國出show係好pay過本國明星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5.上海人<br />\n中國其中一個金融中心，又有自己語言文化，儼如一個獨立國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n6.其他一線城市嘅户籍居民<br />\n一線城市嘅户籍喺中國好吃香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n7.中國少數民族<br />\n有政策優待，例如考生高考總分加十零分，計生政策寬鬆D&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n8.其他二三線城市户籍居民<br />\n冇農村咁慘，但户籍唔吃香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n9.東北三省居民<br />\n投資不過山海關呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n10.河南人<br />\n雖然俾全中國睇唔起，但起碼叫有D存在感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n11.農村户籍人口"},{"pid":"ad88d29451824b01f9ebd397bec3da2abc0ed21a","tid":2152060,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T02:11:24.000Z","msg":"true<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}